# CurveLens Gold cron template — intentionally non-executable.
#
# Gold is experimental. Do not register or enable schedules from this file.
# Before production, replace this placeholder with a reviewed Section-64
# downloader flow and an isolated agent turn that explicitly sets:
#
#   CCVM_PRODUCT=gold
#   # data defaults automatically to ccvm/data/products/gold
#
# The future schedule must read AGENTS.md plus deployments/gold/AGENTS.md,
# acquire and verify the exact Section 64 bulletin, and invoke
# `$curvelens-daily-analysis` for its internal trade date. It must resume
# persisted state, omit EIA petroleum jobs, perform no delivery by default, and
# ship disabled for explicit approval. A bare Python cron is unsupported.
